81
00:07:41,595 --> 00:07:44,462
<i>Chris was born in Cheshire, England...</i>

82
00:07:44,531 --> 00:07:47,898
<i>to an upper-class family in 1904..</i>

83
00:07:51,772 --> 00:07:57,210
<i>His mother, Kathleen,
